'''Domain Karsh''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Notable members of Domain Karsh included [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commander]] [[Komm Karsh]] and [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Hreven Karsh]]. During the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], Domain Karsh remained loyal to [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]], and their ships were part of the flotilla that was sent to attack [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]].

